creator: Karaoke Smart
descriptionHtml:
Live singing with Kanto. Sing wherever you want and whenever you want. Choose your favorite songs and sing with high sound quality.

Enjoy thousands of karaoke songs in special playlists for every moment and occasion. Kanto constantly adds trending songs to the catalog. Discover what's new!

* Be part of the ranking
Have fun singing, share your recording, get followers and stand out in our community in Latin America.

* Stands out on the channel
Sing and appear in our channel of featured recordings in Latin America.

* Create a duet
Record yourself singing a part of a song so that others can complete it with you.

* Join a duet
Choose your favorite song, explore the invitations and complete a duet with another person.

* Create new music
Create new versions of your favorite songs solo or with other singers.

* Sing on your TV
Search Kanto on your TV and connect the mobile app to interact with your friends sending stickers like tomatoes and more!


Subscriptions

• Subscribe to have full access to the catalog of songs and Kanto features.
• Subscriptions are monthly or yearly.
• Payment will be charged to the Google Play account in the purchase confirmation.
• The subscription is automatically renewed unless the automatic renewal is deactivated at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
• The renewal account will be charged within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period and the cost of the renewal will be identified.
• Subscriptions can be managed by the user and automatic renewal can be deactivated by entering the User Account Settings after the purchase.
• Any unused portion of a free trial period will be lost when the user purchases a subscription.
• You can read our Terms and Conditions and Privacy Policy at https://www.kanto.co/termsAndConditions
descriptionShort: Sing, record your voice and share it. Become a star!

title: Kanto

creator: Karaoke Smart
descriptionHtml:
Live singing with Kanto. Sing wherever you want and whenever you want. Choose your favorite songs and sing with high sound quality.

Enjoy thousands of karaoke songs in special playlists for every moment and occasion. Kanto constantly adds trending songs to the catalog. Discover what's new!

* Be part of the ranking
Have fun singing, share your recording, get followers and stand out in our community in Latin America.

* Stands out on the channel
Sing and appear in our channel of featured recordings in Latin America.

* Create a duet
Record yourself singing a part of a song so that others can complete it with you.

* Join a duet
Choose your favorite song, explore the invitations and complete a duet with another person.

* Create new music
Create new versions of your favorite songs solo or with other singers.

* Sing on your TV
Search Kanto on your TV and connect the mobile app to interact with your friends sending stickers like tomatoes and more!


Subscriptions

• Subscribe to have full access to the catalog of songs and Kanto features.
• Subscriptions are monthly or yearly.
• Payment will be charged to the Google Play account in the purchase confirmation.
• The subscription is automatically renewed unless the automatic renewal is deactivated at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
• The renewal account will be charged within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period and the cost of the renewal will be identified.
• Subscriptions can be managed by the user and automatic renewal can be deactivated by entering the User Account Settings after the purchase.
• Any unused portion of a free trial period will be lost when the user purchases a subscription.
• You can read our Terms and Conditions and Privacy Policy at https://www.kanto.co/termsAndConditions
descriptionShort: Sing, record your voice and share it. Become a star!
